{"tid":1190169,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook將暫停在華為手機預裝應用程式","createTime":"2019-06-07T07:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T07:36:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6008345c2e0a2688026ac3ae65e61b49791e0592","tid":1190169,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:32:43.000Z","msg":"中國智能手機製造商華為頻遭封殺，繼Google後，《路透》報道，社交平台Facebook將暫停在華為手機上預裝應用程式。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述Facebook指，已擁有華為手機的客戶仍可使用其應用程式並接收更新，但新的華為手機將無法再預裝Facebook、WhatsApp和Instagram等應用程式，惟Facebook沒有透露何時開始暫停預裝，而華為未有就報道作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n面對一連串封殺，早前華為表示，公司已為美國的行動做好準備，必定會解決任何中斷問題。但報道提到，部分歐洲和亞洲的客戶表示，由於華為充斥不明朗因素，故不願意購買其手機。有分析師預計，華為智能手機銷量將會大幅下滑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1559892062359&amp;issue=20190607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1559892062359%26issue%3D20190607&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8upS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=41624ea2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1559892062359%26issue%3D20190607&h=ef5660d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1559892062359&amp;issue=20190607</a>"},{"pid":"661327715e43ff38ae27cf7b55f7f530e57eb9d2","tid":1190169,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"反正中國都用唔到Facebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}